<lb ed="J" n="0921a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:div type="xu"><cb:mulu type="序" level="1">序</cb:mulu><head>善<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>師語錄敘</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0921a02"/><p xml:id="pJ39p0921a0201"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>條白棒特標
<lb ed="J" n="0921a03"/>單<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>機大用惟能
<lb ed="J" n="0921a04"/>截斷<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>乾坤直接大乘
<lb ed="J" n="0921a05"/>根<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>心宗後來枝繁
<lb ed="J" n="0921a06"/>葉茂門戶各開家聲獨振異見
<lb ed="J" n="0921a07"/>風起主法者喜以文字詩韻備
<lb ed="J" n="0921a08"/>極<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>鬧門庭不念祖
<lb ed="J" n="0921a09"/>道陸<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>善權和尚者履踐純
<lb ed="J" n="0921a10"/>實行<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>相應荷。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0921a11"/><p xml:id="pJ39p0921a1101"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>人缽袋拔露胸襟體用
<lb ed="J" n="0921a12"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>與而奪或縱而擒怒罵
<lb ed="J" n="0921a13"/>嬉笑無非妙用遇緣而說如藥
<lb ed="J" n="0921a14"/>麼<unclear></unclear>稱性而用殺活皆全故使
<lb ed="J" n="0921a15"/>內外<unclear></unclear>向遠近風皈真可謂末
<lb ed="J" n="0921a16"/>法時<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>與臨濟之道者善權
<lb ed="J" n="0921a17"/>和尚<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>造人之不齊緣
<lb ed="J" n="0921a18"/>事早畢門弟子將師語錄刊行
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J39.B469.0921b" n="0921b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0921b01"/>幸孚世龍公默念心法難忘徵
<lb ed="J" n="0921b02"/>予敘<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>簡子因久交故不揣
<lb ed="J" n="0921b03"/>鄙髦<unclear></unclear>敘概耳其師本分以待
<lb ed="J" n="0921b04"/>作家另行拈出云爾。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0921b05"/><p xml:id="pJ39p0921b0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:1em">時
<lb ed="J" n="0921b06" type="honorific"/>康熙戊辰年仲春月望日吉旦
<lb ed="J" n="0921b07"/>中憲大夫前知雲南府事郡
<lb ed="J" n="0921b08"/>人吳之瑋沭手拜撰</p></cb:div>
